text: "Only Human" is a song by Australian singer-songwriter Delta Goodrem. The stripped-back piano ballad was written by Goodrem, Vince Pizzinga and Pete Nappi. It was released as a digital download on 13 March 2015 to coincide with her return to Neighbours for the show's 30th anniversary.
